  "body": "It is simple, every 10K blocks, a special block is produced.\r\n\r\nThe special block has the balances of every wallet, once it is mined, its broadcasted to the network and validated as any other block and added to the blockchain.\r\n\r\nYou can then, delete all the blocks behind that special block, because it contains all the information of the balances and contracts previously created.",
