    "body": "The state of Ethereum is about 15GB raw data. Receipts (which contain the log entries) are maybe about 100GB. That would be one big block :P You also have the issue of deep-er reorgs. PoW does not guarantee finality, so in theory you could have a deeper reorg than your snapshot block.\r\n\r\nAll in all, yes, please head over to the magicians to discuss these ideas.",
